description.plain: Dirtyphonics is an electronic band that consists of Charly Barranger, Julien “PitchIn” Corrales, & Julien “Pho” Lignon. Thomas Desbouvrie & James “Youthstar” Davies were also apart of the band but left on other terms.

body.plain: Dirtyphonics is an electronic band that consists of Charly Barranger, Julien “PitchIn” Corrales, & Julien “Pho” Lignon. Thomas Desbouvrie & James “Youthstar” Davies were also apart of the band but left on other terms.

I forgot the times before it stood for something
Now I watch the feeling grow, feelings wrapped around my soul, I said

description.plain: “Scary Monsters And Nice Sprites (Dirtyphonics Remix)” is the 1st remix (and 4th track) off of the EP/Remix EP “More Monsters And Sprites”. It’s a remix of “Scary Monsters And Nice Sprites”, and is off of the EP of the same name. This track is more hyper than the original, with beats ranging from slow to fast.
